content: Hello! I recently signed up to be a front desk volunteer but I don’t know where to go or what to do
I'm not sure what this exactly. Is it local in person? We just do online/from home volunteering on this server. But if it's for an online team here, I'd just need to know which one to help you.
That’s the link I was given
I don’t really know anything else about the event
I was hopeful that it would be online, but it looks like it’s GA specific

Ah, yes, it does look like a virtual meeting first, but not national, so it's not us. You could attend the online training and see if it's for an in person event or something online that's not related to our work here in the server. But it's not us, I can tell that by looking.
It's 2024 GA Victory specific, so hard to say what they're doing exactly.
Without attending a virtual training event, which looks like that's what this link is.

For online only, just choose one of these trainings and those all route back to here to do your work on a team channel within this server:

https://events.democrats.org/?is_high_priority=true
